My new album Obnoxious Theater Kid is available for streaming on all platforms now! I’m so so excited to finally show everyone what we have been working on for the last 13 months. This was a massive album with 17 tracks and so many collaborators. Thank you so much to my producers @jonathanymusic @villainousmedia @samhaftmusic @kylendeporter @trewatsonmusic @ryanlafford , and to everyone who lent their talent and hopped on a track! @familyjules7x @kaggyfilms @samhaftmusic @eddiecorreajr @withakinsta @keithsilverstein @drewryanscott @themelalee @noahmanumaleuga @christinecabanos ! Huge shoutout to @mechibaz for the amazing cover art! Thank you all so much for your support. It’s amazing to be able to do all this without a record label so every stream is greatly appreciated. ❤️
